Sentinel v0.9.5.100

Sprint: Ground Truth Alignment Guard

Purpose:
- Prevent contextual inference rows from being treated as character-level OCR evidence.
- Separate Alignment Context Gaps from true Character Fidelity drift.
- Keep Character ReOCR focused on safe row-level matches only.

Validation:
- pytest -q tests/smoke/test_alignment_guard_100.py
- python -m py_compile ground_truth_validator.py inference/context_engine.py parser/targeted_character_reocr.py
- zip integrity check

Commit command:
git add .
git commit -m "fix(data-guard): separate alignment gaps from character verification"

tag command:
git tag -a v0.9.5.100 -m "v0.9.5.100 Ground Truth Alignment Guard"
